// DesignToolbar
// Toolbar for the design editor with undo/redo, zoom controls, PNG export,
// and PNG clipboard copy.

Undo/redo availability is re-read on every sceneVersion change via
getEditorRefs().undo.canUndo/canRedo.

FUNCTION DesignToolbar(onToggleLayers, onToggleProperties, ...) -> JSX  EXPORT
  CALLS: renderNodesToImage (renderNodesToImage)
  Reads canUndo/canRedo from store editor refs on sceneVersion change.
  Renders: undo/redo buttons; zoom-out, zoom level display, zoom-in; layers
  and properties panel toggles; export PNG button; copy PNG button.

---

FUNCTION handleUndo() -> void
  Calls store.undoAction().

---

FUNCTION handleRedo() -> void
  Calls store.redoAction().

---

FUNCTION handleZoomIn() -> void
  Calls store.applyZoom(+100) at viewport center.

---

FUNCTION handleZoomOut() -> void
  Calls store.applyZoom(-100) at viewport center.

---

FUNCTION handleExportPng() -> void
  Calls renderNodesToImage to get a PNG blob.
  Creates a temporary blob URL, triggers a download link click, revokes the URL.

---

FUNCTION handleCopyPng() -> void
  Calls renderNodesToImage to get a PNG blob.
  Writes the blob to the clipboard via ClipboardItem API.
